36 experience with a qualified clinical supervisor, as defined in section 337.600, within the same
37 time frame prescribed in this subsection, the applicant shall be eligible for application of

HB 3007 12
38 licensure at three thousand hours and shall be furnished a certificate by the state committee
39 for social workers acknowledging the completion of said additional hours;
40 [(3)] (4) The applicant has achieved a passing score, as defined by the committee, on
